Used Reference (English): Composer of {MEDIUM} and {SYMPHONY_IMPOSSIBLE_TO_PLAY} as well as dozens of tracks across the Homestuck discography, and artist behind several independent albums whose tracks were recompiled and featured as the soundtrack for {PSYCHOLONIALS}.
String Value: Compositora de {MEDIUM} y {SYMPHONY_IMPOSSIBLE_TO_PLAY} al igual que docenas de canciones a través de la discografía de Homestuck, y la artista detrás de varios álbumes independientes cuyas canciones fueron recopiladas y usadas como la banda sonora para {PSYCHOLONIALS}.

Used Reference (English): Artist behind {PERFECTLY_GENERIC_ALBUM} and more, and creator of crossover fanventure {DELTASTUCK}. Releases under a number of aliases.
String Value: Artista detrás de {PERFECTLY_GENERIC_ALBUM} entre otros, y creadora de la fanventura crossover {DELTASTUCK}. Lanza álbumes bajo una variedad de nombres.

Used Reference (English): Renowned for {SBURBAN_JUNGLE}, his official solo album {MOBIUS_TRIP_AND_HADRON_KALEIDO} and many other hit Homestuck releases, Bowman has gone on to create his own expansive personal discography since.
String Value: Reconicido por {SBURBAN_JUNGLE}, su album solo oficial {MOBIUS_TRIP_AND_HADRON_KALEIDO} y muchos otros hits en la discográfica de Homestuck, Bowman ha continuado desde entonces con su extensa discografía personal.

Used Reference (English): Artist behind tracks across a wide variety of fan albums (where she's credited as {KAL_LA_KAL_LA}), with two experimental noise-poetry albums by her own solo release.
String Value: Artista creadora de varias canciones en una gama de álbumes fan (donde es acreditada como {KAL_LA_KAL_LA}), con dos álbumes de poesía sonora en su haber.

Used Reference (English): Co-creator of the webcomic {INHOSPITABLE}, and musician with a history spanning half a decade. Plural internet artist.
String Value: Co-creadora del webcomic [INHOSPITABLE], y música con un catálogo que abarca media década. Artista plural de internet.

Used Reference (English): Rock composer behind hit 2011 release {STRIFE} and overall guitarist and musician behind a whole host of memorable tracks. He's gone on to release the 2017 sequel {STRIFE_2} and a variety of other collaborative tracks since Homestuck!
String Value: Compositor roquero detrás del lanzamiento hit de 2011 {STRIFE} y en general guitarrista y músico detrás de una gran cantidad de canciones memorables. ¡Desde entonces ha lanzado la secuela de 2017 {STRIFE_2} y una variedad de otras canciones colaborativas tras Homestuck!

Used Reference (English): Artist of well over 100 tracks in Homestuck's musical canon (including the elusive {PENUMBRA_PHANTASM}), Toby Fox went on to compose the much-renowned soundtracks to his games {UNDERTALE_AND_DELTARUNE}, firmly planting his place in modern game and internet history.
String Value: Un artista con más de 100 canciones en el canon musical de Homestuck (incluyendo el elusivo {PENUMBRA_PHANTASM}), Toby Fox siguió a componer las renombradas bandas sonoras de sus juegos {UNDERTALE_AND_DELTARUNE}, plantando firmemente su lugar en la historia moderna de los videojuegos e Internet.
